"""
NEURAL NODE TEMPLATE SYSTEM - SECURE PERSONAL MARKETING
=========================================================
Templates are cryptographic representations of a person's node fingerprint
They can be used by multiple marketing models WITHOUT exposing raw data
The template stays on PERSON'S device - only derived features are shared

Key Innovation: 
- Template = Mathematical representation of node state
- Person controls what features are extracted
- Marketing models receive TEMPLATE FEATURES, not raw data
- Template cannot be reverse-engineered to get personal data
- One template can serve hundreds of marketing models
"""

import hashlib
